data.title: Sendex
data.description: Unisex adult sweatshirt. Made in a combination of brushed organic cotton and RPET polyester 280gsm. Collar, cuffs and waistband in 2x1 rib knit, with stitched shoulders and eco label. GOTS (Global Organic Textile Standard) and GRS (Global Recycled Standard) certified, certifying the eco-friendly origin of the material used in the manufacture of the product. With distinctive eco label. Available in a wide range of colours and in sizes XS, S, M, L, XL, XXL, 3XL.

data.title: Harnix

Collar, cuffs and waistband in 2x1 rib knit, with stitched shoulders and eco label. GOTS (Global Organic Textile Standard) and GRS (Global Recycled Standard) certified, certifying the eco-friendly origin of the material used in the manufacture of the product. Available in a wide range of colours and in sizes XS, S, M, L, XL, XXL, 3XL.

data.title: Mesiox
data.description: Unisex jacket in warm and soft 155g/m2 RPET micro polar fleece with anti-pilling treatment. Material made from recycled plastic, to encourage the reuse of plastic waste and contribute to the sustainability of the planet.  Zipper closure in neck and elastic waist. Available in sizes S, M, L, XL, XXL, with eco label.

data.title: Diston

data.title: Scola

Eco emblem on the bottom hem of the garment. With zipper closure and including chest and side pockets with invisible zip closure and matching pullers.  Available in a wide range of colours and in sizes S, M, L, XL, XXL.

data.title: Grea
data.description: Unisex hooded sweatshirt with washed jeans effect, making each piece unique and unrepeatable. Kangaroo pocket, with extra wide elastic bands for a perfect fit. Contrast color in the elastic bands of cuffs and hem. Made in 100% combed cotton 280g/m2. Soft touch and modern cut, with adjustable flat strings and embroidered eyelets, avoiding the use of metal. Double stitching for durability and resistance to intensive wear. Easily removable label and available in sizes XS, S, M, L, XL and XXL.

data.title: Truyi
data.description: Bicolor unisex sweatshirt with washed and dyed effect on the garment, making each piece unique and unrepeatable. Made in 100% Ring Spun combed cotton 280g/m2. Soft touch and modern cut. Cuff and hem with extra wide elastic bands for a perfect fit. Narrow round neck in 2x2 rib. Double stitchings for durability and resistance to intensive wear. Easily removable label and available in sizes XS, S, M, L, XL and XXL.
